void project_renderdata ( Render *  re,
void(*)(const float *, float mat[][4], float *)  projectfunc,
int  do_pano,
float  xoffs,
int   UNUSEDdo_buckets 
)

This adds the hcs coordinates to vertices. It iterates over all vertices, halos and faces. After the conversion, we clip in hcs.

Elsewhere, all primites are converted to vertices. Called in

  • envmapping (envmap.c)
  • shadow buffering (shadbuf.c)
